<!-- MainCellStart --><TD VALIGN='TOP'><CENTER><table border=0 cellpadding=5 bgcolor=#DDDDDD width=50% background='/images/table-head-bg.jpg'><tr><td background=''><table border=0 cellpadding=5 bgcolor=#BB0000 width=100%><tr><td width=50% background='/images/table-bg.jpg'><b><font size=+3 color=#FFF000><center>What Is EverGuild?<center></font></b></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></center><HR SIZE=1 WIDTH=80%></CENTER><BR><B><U><FONT SIZE=+1>About EverGuild</FONT></U></B><BR>

<P>&nbsp&nbsp EverGuild is an EverQuest Guild Managment, Organization, and
Communications Utility currently under development which, when completed, will provide
guild masters with a powerful tool by which to maintain there guild.  Here
is a small listing of some of the key features that the completed version
of EverGuild is planning to have :</p>

 <ul>
 <li>Guild Management and Control System
 <li>Live Chat and Meeting System
 <li>Personal/Group Messageing System
 <li>Guild and Sub-Guild Message Board System
 <li>Calendar and Event Planning System
 <li>Guild Voting Booth System
 <li>Intra-Guild Interaction (aliances/Enemies) Support System
 </ul><br>

 <center><image src="eg_main.jpg"></center><br>

You can access the Online <a href=eg_help.htm>EverGuild Help File</a> for more information.

